South African Mines Lobby ANC on Nationalization Policy, Business Day Says

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-06-28T05:21:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/south-african-mines-lobby-anc-on-nationalization-policy-business-day-says.html
South Africa ’s Chamber of Mines
started lobbying members of the  African National Congress  for
their support against the nationalization of the country’s
mines, Business Day reported, citing the chamber.  The group criticized senior ANC officials for failing to
rein in members backing the policy, the Johannesburg-based
newspaper cited Bheki Sibiya, the chamber’s chief executive
officer, as saying.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
